trans-unit.source: Represents a window that supports content navigation.
trans-unit.target: Representerer et vindu som støtter innhold navigeringen.

trans-unit.source: NavigationWindow derives from <xref:System.Windows.Window> and extends it with the ability to navigate to and display content.
trans-unit.target: NavigationWindow er avledet fra <xref:System.Windows.Window>og utvider muligheten til å navigere til, og Vis innhold.</xref:System.Windows.Window>

trans-unit.source: Content can be any [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winfx](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-winfx-md.md)] object or [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_html](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-html-md.md)] file.
trans-unit.target: Innhold kan være [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winfx](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-winfx-md.md)] objektet eller [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_html](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-html-md.md)] filen.

trans-unit.source: In general, however, a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Page> object is the preferred way to package content for navigation.
trans-unit.target: Generelt imidlertid en <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Page>objektet er den foretrukne måten å pakkens innhold for navigasjon.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Page>

trans-unit.source: Content can be navigated to by setting the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Source%2A> property with the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] for the desired content.
trans-unit.target: Innhold kan bli sendt til ved å angi den <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Source%2A>egenskapen med den [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] for ønsket innhold.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Source%2A>

trans-unit.source: Additionally, content can be navigated to by using one of the following overloads of the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%2A> method: - <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> - <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%28System.Uri%2CSystem.Object%29> When content is navigated to by [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)], NavigationWindow will return an object that contains the content.
trans-unit.target: I tillegg innholdet kan navigeres til ved hjelp av følgende overlastingene av den <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%2A>metoden:- <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%28System.Uri%29>- <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%28System.Uri%2CSystem.Object%29>når innholdet navigeres til av [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)], NavigationWindow kommer til å returnere et objekt som inneholder innholdet.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%28System.Uri%2CSystem.Object%29> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%2A>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Navigation by [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] also supports navigation to a content fragment.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Navigering etter [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] støtter også navigering til et innhold fragment.

trans-unit.source: See <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.FragmentNavigation>.
trans-unit.target: Se <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.FragmentNavigation>.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.FragmentNavigation>

trans-unit.source: Alternatively, content can be navigated to by using one of the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%2A> method overloads that accepts an object: - <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%28System.Object%29> - <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%28System.Object%2CSystem.Object%29> The lifetime of a navigation can be tracked through the following events: - <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigating> - <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigated> - <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.NavigationProgress> - <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.NavigationFailed> - <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.NavigationStopped> - <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.LoadCompleted> - <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.FragmentNavigation>.
trans-unit.target: Du kan også innholdet kan navigeres til ved hjelp av den <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%2A>metoden overlastingene som godtar et objekt:- <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%28System.Object%29>- <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%28System.Object%2CSystem.Object%29>levetiden for navigering kan spores gjennom følgende hendelser:- <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigating>- <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigated>- <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.NavigationProgress>- <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.NavigationFailed>- <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.NavigationStopped>- <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.LoadCompleted>- <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.FragmentNavigation>.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.FragmentNavigation> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.LoadCompleted> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.NavigationStopped> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.NavigationFailed> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.NavigationProgress> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigated> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigating> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%28System.Object%2CSystem.Object%29> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%28System.Object%29> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%2A>

trans-unit.source: Not all events are raised each time that a navigation occurs; the set of events that are raised is determined by the type of navigation that occurs (content or content fragment) and how the navigation completes (canceled, stopped, or failed).
trans-unit.target: Ikke alle hendelser aktiveres hver gang en navigering; Sett med hendelser som aktiveres er avhengig av hva slags navigering som forekommer (innhold eller innhold fragment) og hvordan navigeringen er fullført (avbrutt stoppet eller mislyktes).

trans-unit.source: The following figure illustrates the sequence in which these events will fire: ![Page navigation flow chart](~/add/media/navigationoverviewfigure11.png "Page navigation flow chart") During or after a navigation, NavigationWindow provides information about the content that is being navigated to, including the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] of the content being navigated to (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Source%2A>), the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] of the current content (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.CurrentSource%2A>), and an object that contains the content that was navigated to (<xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContentControl.Content%2A>).
trans-unit.target: Illustrasjonen nedenfor viser rekkefølgen som disse hendelser skal aktiveres: ![siden navigasjon flyten diagrammet](~/add/media/navigationoverviewfigure11.png "siden navigasjon flyten diagrammet") under eller etter navigering NavigationWindow gir informasjon om innholdet som blir navigeres til, inkludert i [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] på innholdet som navigeres til (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Source%2A>), [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] for gjeldende innhold (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.CurrentSource%2A>), og et objekt som har innhold som er mulig å navigere til (<xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContentControl.Content%2A>).</xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContentControl.Content%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.CurrentSource%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Source%2A>

trans-unit.source: When content is navigated to, NavigationWindow records the navigation as an entry in navigation history.
trans-unit.target: Når innholdet navigeres til, registrerer NavigationWindow navigasjon som en oppføring i loggen for navigasjon.

trans-unit.source: An entry is added to back navigation history when either a new navigation occurs, by calling the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%2A> method, or by navigating to an entry in forward navigation history, by calling <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.GoForward%2A>.
trans-unit.target: En oppføring er lagt til tilbake historikk for navigasjon når enten en ny navigering, ved å ringe det <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%2A>metode, eller ved å navigere til en oppføring i Videresend navigasjon loggen ved å kalle <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.GoForward%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.GoForward%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%2A>

trans-unit.source: An entry is added to forward navigation history by navigating to an entry in back navigation history, by calling <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.GoBack%2A>.
trans-unit.target: En oppføring legges til Videresend navigasjon historikk ved å navigere til en oppføring i tilbake navigasjon loggen ved å kalle <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.GoBack%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.GoBack%2A>

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.CanGoBack%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.CanGoForward%2A> report whether there are entries in back and forward navigation history, respectively.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.CanGoBack%2A>og <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.CanGoForward%2A>rapportere om det er oppføringer i tilbake og fremover navigasjon historikk henholdsvis.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.CanGoForward%2A></xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.CanGoBack%2A>

trans-unit.source: The first time that one piece of content is navigated to from another piece of content, NavigationWindow automatically displays a navigation [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] that allows users to navigate back and forwards through navigation history.
trans-unit.target: Første gang som en del av innholdet navigeres til fra en annen type innhold, NavigationWindow viser automatisk navigering [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] som gjør at brukere kan gå tilbake og videresender via navigasjon historikk.

trans-unit.source: You can configure when the navigation [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] is shown by setting the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.ShowsNavigationUI%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Du kan konfigurere når navigeringen [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] vises ved å angi den <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.ShowsNavigationUI%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.ShowsNavigationUI%2A>

trans-unit.source: The most recent entry in back navigation history can be removed by calling <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.RemoveBackEntry%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Den siste oppføringen i tilbake navigasjon loggen kan fjernes ved å kalle <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.RemoveBackEntry%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.RemoveBackEntry%2A>

trans-unit.source: NavigationWindow does not store an instance of a content object in navigation history.
trans-unit.target: NavigationWindow lagres ikke en forekomst av en innholdspakke objektet i loggen for navigasjon.

trans-unit.source: Instead, NavigationWindow creates a new instance of the content object each time it is navigated to by using navigation history.
trans-unit.target: I stedet oppretter NavigationWindow en ny forekomst av innhold objektet hver gang det navigeres til ved hjelp av navigasjon historikk.

trans-unit.source: This behavior is designed to avoid excessive memory consumption when large numbers and large pieces of content are being navigated to.
trans-unit.target: Dette er utformet for å unngå mye minneforbruk under store tall og store typer innhold som hendelsene til.

trans-unit.source: Consequently, the state of the content is not remembered from one navigation to the next.
trans-unit.target: Derfor er ikke tilstanden på innholdet husker fra én navigering til neste.

trans-unit.source: However, [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] provides several techniques by which you can store a piece of state for a piece of content in navigation history.
trans-unit.target: Imidlertid [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] inneholder flere metoder som du kan lagre en del av tilstand for innhold i loggen for navigasjon.

trans-unit.source: Using <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.AddBackEntry%2A>, you can also remember multiple sets of state for a single page instance.
trans-unit.target: Ved hjelp av <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.AddBackEntry%2A>, du kan også huske flere sett med tilstanden for en enkelt side-forekomst.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.AddBackEntry%2A>

trans-unit.source: NavigationWindow is one of two navigators in [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)], the other being <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>.
trans-unit.target: NavigationWindow er en av to navigatorer i [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)], den andre som <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>

trans-unit.source: Essentially, navigator is a class supports navigation and navigation history.
trans-unit.target: Navigatoren er, en klasse støtter navigering og navigasjon historikk.

trans-unit.source: Visually, [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xbapsharpplural-md.md)] use [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-ie7-md.md)] as a navigator, to provide an integrated user experience.
trans-unit.target: Visuelt, [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xbapsharpplural-md.md)] Bruk [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-ie7-md.md)] som en navigatoren til en integrert brukeropplevelsen.

trans-unit.source: However, [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xbapsharpplural-md.md)] actually use NavigationWindow as the navigator; the <xref:System.Windows.Application.MainWindow%2A> property of an [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] running in [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-ie7-md.md)] will return a reference to the NavigationWindow, and the navigation history that is managed by the NavigationWindow is integrated with the navigation history that is managed by [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-ie7-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: Imidlertid [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xbapsharpplural-md.md)] faktisk bruker NavigationWindow som navigatoren; den <xref:System.Windows.Application.MainWindow%2A>for en [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] kjører i [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-ie7-md.md)] vil returnere en referanse til NavigationWindow og navigasjon loggen som administreres av NavigationWindow er integrert med navigasjon loggen som administreres av [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-ie7-md.md)].</xref:System.Windows.Application.MainWindow%2A>

trans-unit.source: **Content Model:** NavigationWindow is a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContentControl>, which means that NavigationWindow can contain content such as text, images, or panels.
trans-unit.target: **Innholdsmodellen:** NavigationWindow er en <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContentControl>, noe som betyr at NavigationWindow kan inneholde innhold som tekst, bilder eller paneler.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContentControl>

trans-unit.source: Also, NavigationWindow is a root element and, consequently, cannot be part of another element's content.
trans-unit.target: Også NavigationWindow er et rotelement, og derfor kan ikke være en del av en annen elementinnhold.

trans-unit.source: For more information about the content model for <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Button>, see [WPF Content Model](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: For mer informasjon om innholdsmodellen for <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Button>, se [WPF innhold modellen](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Button>

trans-unit.source: Customizing the NavigationWindow Control To apply the same property settings to multiple NavigationWindow controls, use the <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.Style%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Tilpasse den NavigationWindow kontrollen til gjelder samme egenskapsinnstillingene flere NavigationWindow kontroller, bruk av <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.Style%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.Style%2A>

trans-unit.source: You can modify the default <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ControlTemplate> to give the control a unique appearance.
trans-unit.target: Du kan endre standard <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ControlTemplate>Gi kontrollen unikt utseende.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.ControlTemplate>

trans-unit.source: For more information about creating a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ControlTemplate>, see [Customizing the Appearance of an Existing Control by Creating a ControlTemplate](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: For mer informasjon om hvordan du oppretter en <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ControlTemplate>, se [tilpasse utseendet til en eksisterende kontroll ved å opprette en ControlTemplate](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).</xref:System.Windows.Controls.ControlTemplate>

trans-unit.source: To see the parts and states that are specific to the NavigationWindow, see [NavigationWindow Styles and Templates](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil se delene og statusene som er spesifikke for NavigationWindow, kan du se [NavigationWindow stiler og maler](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that indicates whether a <xref href="System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow"></xref> isolates external [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-xaml-md.md)] content within a partial trust security sandbox (with default Internet zone permission set).
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir om en <xref href="System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow"> </xref> isolat ekstern [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-xaml-md.md)] innhold i en delvis klarering sikkerhet sandkassen (med standard Internett-sone tillatelse angitt).

trans-unit.source: External content is [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)] content that is not included with an application as either a resource file or a content file (for more information, see [WPF Application Resource, Content, and Data Files](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)).
trans-unit.target: Eksternt innhold er [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)] innhold som ikke er inkludert i en applikasjon som en ressursfil eller innhold fil (for mer informasjon, kan du se [WPF programmet ressursen, innhold og datafiler](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)).

trans-unit.source: When SandboxExternalContent is true, and the content of the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow> is an external [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)] file, the content is loaded into a partial trust security sandbox that is limited to the default Internet zone permission set.
trans-unit.target: Når SandboxExternalContent er true, og innholdet i den <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>er en ekstern [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)] filen innholdet er lastet inn i en delvis klarering sikkerhet sandkassen som er begrenset til standard Internett-sone er angitt.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>

trans-unit.source: Additionally, the external content is loaded into a separate process.
trans-unit.target: Det eksterne innholdet lastes i tillegg til en annen prosess.

trans-unit.source: Consequently, the external content becomes isolated and does not have access to application-scope resources, such as resource dictionaries (for more information, see <xref:System.Windows.ResourceDictionary>).
trans-unit.target: Derfor kan det eksterne innholdet blir isolert og ikke har tilgang til global informasjon ressurser, for eksempel ressursen ordlister (Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, se <xref:System.Windows.ResourceDictionary>).</xref:System.Windows.ResourceDictionary>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow> contains external content only when the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Source%2A> property is set to the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)] for an external [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)] file.
